### Crear una orden (necesita token)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ordenes
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "productoId": 1, "cantidad": 2 },
    { "productoId": 3, "cantidad": 1 }
  ]
}

### Ver mis órdenes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ordenes
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Ver detalle de una orden
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ordenes/1
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Actualizar status (solo admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/ordenes/1/status
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmada"
}

### Ver todas las órdenes (solo admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ordenes/todas
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI